body: [screenParticipant] can now only be successfully called if the owner of the survey provides a valid signature. We’ve created a new ClosedSurveyV6.sol to handle any reward token that follows the ERC-20 standard, meaning that you can deploy the contract and fund it with a token like GoodDollar(G$), and the distribution will work well.
